{"id":1,"name":"EV001","note":"","pages":[{"conditions":{"actorId":1,"actorValid":false,"itemId":1,"itemValid":false,"selfSwitchCh":"A","selfSwitchValid":false,"switch1Id":1,"switch1Valid":false,"switch2Id":1,"switch2Valid":false,"variableId":1,"variableValid":false,"variableValue":0},"directionFix":false,"image":{"characterIndex":0,"characterName":"","direction":2,"pattern":0,"tileId":0},"list":[{"code":241,"indent":0,"parameters":[{"name":"Worldbearer Matirx","volume":90,"pitch":100,"pan":0}]},{"code":122,"indent":0,"parameters":[200,200,0,0,0]},{"code":121,"indent":0,"parameters":[3,3,0]},{"code":231,"indent":0,"parameters":[1,"control intro",0,0,0,0,100,100,255,0]},{"code":231,"indent":0,"parameters":[10,"tips1",0,0,0,0,100,100,0,0]},{"code":231,"indent":0,"parameters":[11,"tips2",0,0,0,0,100,100,0,0]},{"code":231,"indent":0,"parameters":[12,"tips3",0,0,0,0,100,100,0,0]},{"code":231,"indent":0,"parameters":[13,"tips4",0,0,0,0,100,100,0,0]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,2,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["玩前提示："]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["是个没完成的测试版，详情看更新日志"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["有问题统统记下来，打完后统一找作者算账（？"]},{"code":102,"indent":0,"parameters":[["正常流程","跳过前情"],1,0,2,1]},{"code":402,"indent":0,"parameters":[0,"正常流程"]},{"code":235,"indent":1,"parameters":[10]},{"code":235,"indent":1,"parameters":[11]},{"code":235,"indent":1,"parameters":[12]},{"code":235,"indent":1,"parameters":[13]},{"code":0,"indent":1,"parameters":[]},{"code":402,"indent":0,"parameters":[1,"跳过前情"]},{"code":242,"indent":1,"parameters":[10]},{"code":235,"indent":1,"parameters":[10]},{"code":235,"indent":1,"parameters":[11]},{"code":235,"indent":1,"parameters":[12]},{"code":235,"indent":1,"parameters":[13]},{"code":235,"indent":1,"parameters":[1]},{"code":355,"indent":1,"parameters":["SceneManager.push(Scene_GoodFortune);"]},{"code":201,"indent":1,"parameters":[0,3,6,5,0,0]},{"code":0,"indent":1,"parameters":[]},{"code":404,"indent":0,"parameters":[]},{"code":211,"indent":0,"parameters":[0]},{"code":231,"indent":0,"parameters":[1,"black",0,0,0,0,100,100,255,0]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,2,1]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["<wrap>永劫回归33550337，光历4284年，那刻夏通过炼金术将万敌的思维能力卸载，将灵魂裂成五份注入靛石打造的神躯。"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,2,1]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["<wrap>自那之后不知过了多久……一个若隐若现的声音唤醒了万敌的意识，他发现自己又能思考了，且仍记得这一轮回发生的一切，什么情况？这是哪里？现在是什么时候？"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["mem",2,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["<wrap>能听到吗？"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["mem",2,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["<wrap>……敌？悬锋……漠斯？醒醒——"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["mydei",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["……"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["mem",2,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["<wrap>哎呀……难不成真的要我手动分离……"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["mydei",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["<wrap>白厄？"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["mem",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["<wrap>呀？醒了吗！"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["mem",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["<wrap>抱歉呀，人家不是你心心念念的救世主。真不好意思突然把你唤醒。"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["mydei",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["<wrap>？迷迷？不对，昔涟小姐？"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["mydei",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["<wrap>什么时候再创世？这是哪？你要我做什么？"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["mem",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["<wrap>……呀，万敌还真是一如既往地直接。"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["mem",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["<wrap>你还记得多少？"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["mydei",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["<wrap>第33550337次永劫回归的记忆从我记事起到我裂魂，<br>第33550336次永劫回归的记忆只包括你给我看过的那部分。<br>所以我在哪？"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["mem",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["<wrap>连数字都记得那么清楚……看来，裂魂造成的损伤似乎都恢复了，状态还不错。"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["mem",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["<wrap>你可以把这里当成某人记忆的迷宫。"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["mem",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["<wrap>我的伙伴正在赶来，而我正在为最后一次再创世做准备。却发现你的记忆和另一人的忆质缠在一起，分不开。"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["mem",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["<wrap>如果不把这团乱码整理好，之后再创世可能会出问题。"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["mem",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["<wrap>我不敢强行把你们分离，又叫不醒属于另一个人的意识……所以人家就把你喊醒，试试看你能不能从内部解开它。"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["mydei",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["<wrap>“另一个人”？哼……总感觉类似的事情不久前发生过一次……"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["mydei",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["<wrap>这片空间，很脆弱。我甚至可以直接——"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["mem",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["<wrap>哎哎哎等一下等一下！！"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["mem",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["<wrap>如你所述，这片忆质确实很脆弱，所以才得更加小心翼翼。为此人家特别强调——"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["mem",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["<wrap>绝对不能在这里战斗！而是要智取！"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["mydei",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["……"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["mydei",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["<wrap>你让纷争半神，智取记忆迷宫。"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["mem",1,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["<wrap>我可没忘记，你在这一轮回是智种学派毕业的。智取某颗智种里发芽的迷宫，没问题的！"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["mydei",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["<wrap>那你大概也没忘，为了对抗来古士，我让阿那克萨戈拉斯把我的脑子卸了。"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["mem",1,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["<wrap>我当然没忘。就在不久前，你的其中一片碎片还在和星穹列车的半神们打架呢！"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["mydei",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["<wrap>……？这不应该，阿那克萨戈拉斯为我设置的程序写了我只能攻击来古士，我为什么要打他们？"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["mem",1,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["<wrap>不知道呢……用伙伴的话来说大概是“哎呀这么大个计算机不出bug都不叫计算机”，也许那一部分的你不愿被静默？"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["mem",1,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["<wrap>无论如何，随着你的五片碎片在记忆的大墓中回归完整，你的灵魂损伤在当前这种状态下是不存在的。我也会帮你的，我能在外部查资料！"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["mydei",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["<wrap>……行吧。怎么开始？"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["mem",1,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["<wrap>深呼吸，潜入他的迷宫吧。"]},{"code":211,"indent":0,"parameters":[1]},{"code":242,"indent":0,"parameters":[10]},{"code":355,"indent":0,"parameters":["SceneManager.push(Scene_GoodFortune);"]},{"code":201,"indent":0,"parameters":[0,3,6,5,0,0]},{"code":0,"indent":0,"parameters":[]}],"moveFrequency":3,"moveRoute":{"list":[{"code":0,"parameters":[]}],"repeat":true,"skippable":false,"wait":false},"moveSpeed":3,"moveType":0,"priorityType":0,"stepAnime":false,"through":false,"trigger":4,"walkAnime":true}],"x":0,"y":0}
]
}